---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Sonar Engagement case study | Expert Voice"
  description="How Sonar Engagement turned a quiet LinkedIn presence into a consistent voice in the Social Value sector, with a growing pipeline of decision-maker connections."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="case-study-page">
    <header class="case-hero">
      <div class="container case-hero-inner">
        <a href="/#cases" class="case-back">← All case studies</a>
        <div class="case-eyebrow">Case study · Social Value Consulting</div>
        <h1 class="display">Sonar Engagement</h1>
        <p class="case-subtitle">From sporadic posting to consistent authority, growing a targeted network of decision-makers and building real visibility in the Social Value sector.</p>

        <div class="case-hero-stats">
          <div class="case-hero-stat">
            <div class="case-hero-stat-num">+551</div>
            <div class="case-hero-stat-label">New followers in 90 days</div>
            <div class="case-hero-stat-context">More than five hundred new people now follow the work, more than doubling the audience in three months.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="case-hero-stat">
            <div class="case-hero-stat-num">+227%</div>
            <div class="case-hero-stat-label">Post engagement</div>
            <div class="case-hero-stat-context">More than three times the likes, comments, and reactions on every post.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="case-hero-stat">
            <div class="case-hero-stat-num">39.5%</div>
            <div class="case-hero-stat-label">Connection acceptance rate</div>
            <div class="case-hero-stat-context">Nearly four in ten relevant decision-makers accept the connection, well above LinkedIn's average.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="case-section-grid">
          <div class="case-section-label">Where they started</div>
          <div class="case-section-body">
            <p>Sonar Engagement is an independent Social Value consultancy with over a decade of experience. There was clear expertise and a distinctive voice already in the room. What was missing was the time and the structure to post consistently on LinkedIn, no outreach system, infrequent content, and a profile that underserved both the reputation and the commercial goals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-section case-section-tinted">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="case-section-grid">
          <div class="case-section-label">How we worked together</div>
          <div class="case-section-body">
            <div class="case-work-grid">
              <article class="case-work-card">
                <div class="case-work-num">01</div>
                <h3>Voice-led content creation</h3>
                <p>A monthly question process captures the stories, opinions and expertise. Posts are written in that voice — opinion-led, personal, with real tension — and scheduled three to four times a week.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="case-work-card">
                <div class="case-work-num">02</div>
                <h3>ICP-targeted outreach</h3>
                <p>Monthly LinkedIn connection campaigns built around the Ideal Client Profile. Targeted by job title, seniority and sector, so every new connection is a relevant decision-maker.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="case-work-card">
                <div class="case-work-num">03</div>
                <h3>Monthly strategy & review</h3>
                <p>Performance is reviewed every month. Content angles get refined based on what's landing, and outreach targeting adjusts to match the results.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="case-work-card">
                <div class="case-work-num">04</div>
                <h3>Always-on growth</h3>
                <p>Connection campaigns run every single month. Hundreds of relevant prospects are added to the network on a continuing basis, ready to be activated whenever the time is right.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="case-section-grid">
          <div class="case-section-label">The result</div>
          <div class="case-section-body">
            <div class="case-result-group">
              <h3>An audience that's growing every day</h3>
              <p>Followers climbed from around 6,380 to 6,926 over 90 days, around four new people every single day. That's not a viral spike, it's the kind of steady compounding growth that comes from showing up consistently in front of the right audience.</p>
              <div class="case-stat-row">
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">6,926</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Total followers</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">And still climbing</div>
                </div>
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">+551</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">New followers</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">In 90 days (+119.5%)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">+4 / day</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Average daily growth</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">Consistent momentum</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="case-result-group">
              <h3>Real conversation, not passive likes</h3>
              <p>Posts went from quiet to genuinely engaged. 305 comments across 90 days means people aren't just scrolling past, they're stopping to react, debate and share. Every comment also extends the reach to the commenter's network, which keeps bringing new decision-makers into view.</p>
              <div class="case-stat-row">
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">50</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Posts published</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">+525% vs. prior period</div>
                </div>
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">1,647</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Total engagements</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">+227%</div>
                </div>
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">305</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Comments</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">+193%</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="case-result-group">
              <h3>A pipeline of warm prospects, built every month</h3>
              <p>The outreach system runs every month, sending invites to a hand-picked list of decision-makers. Acceptance rates well above the LinkedIn average mean hundreds of relevant people are being added to the network on a continuing basis — and they're already seeing the content.</p>
              <div class="case-stat-row">
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">376</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Invites sent</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">Single month</div>
                </div>
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">115</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">New ICP connections</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">Decision-makers reached</div>
                </div>
                <div class="case-stat-card">
                  <div class="case-stat-num">39.5%</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-label">Acceptance rate</div>
                  <div class="case-stat-context">Above LinkedIn average</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-section case-section-callout">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="case-callout">
          <h3>What this all means</h3>
          <p>It's not just a follower count, it's a warm pipeline that grows every month. Every connection added is a potential client who's already said yes once, who now sees the content regularly, and who's one good conversation away from a real opportunity. The system is doing the patient work in the background.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="display">Want this kind of pipeline for your business?</h2>
        <p>Book a 15-minute intro call. No pitch, just a clear read on whether we're a fit.</p>
        <a href="/#book" class="btn-primary">
          <span>Book a call</span>
          <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
